This year, the study of the Association of Russian Managers "Top-1000 Russian Managers" comes out for the 16th time.
As a tool for assessing the professional reputation of Russian managers of the highest echelon, the study summarizes the results of the work of Russian managers for a year, identifying leaders in industries and functional areas.
The initial pool of candidates consists of the winners of last year’s ranking.
